    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Vine stranglers lurk beneath Svellheim's corrupted woodland floors — a tangle of rot-touched vines that has gained predatory intelligence from the Rot's influence. They strike from ambush, erupting from the earth to entangle prey in choking root-grips while draining vitality with poisoned thorns. Their control of the terrain around them makes them especially dangerous in forested or overgrown environments, where they can reshape the battlefield to isolate their victims.</p>",
        "public": ""
